<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="70" >Azrael@Namelessさんは No.5100「Log : NecEpic Quest」で書きました。
>Venenzi嬢に言われた通り、Kazenに暗黒の術を学びに行きます。
>
>☆ I wish to study the dark arts
>
>Kazen Fecae  looks you up and down, his eyes glowing with a
>soft red light. After a moment be begins to speak though his lips
>do not move. 'You wish to study under me? Perhas, if you
>prove yourself to follow the twisted path. If you prove to be as
>coldhearted as I then I will let you become my servant.
>
>☆ I will prove the twisted path
>
>Kazen Fecae says 'The wandering 'knight' Sir Edwin Motte recently
>slew one of my lesser servants. This foolish knave travels from
>town to town pretending to be 'good.' Separate his head from
>his body and return it to me so I may work my magics upon it.
>This fool will become another plaything for me, even in death.
>
>Sir Edwin Motteの首を取ってくれば良いようです。
>Sir Edwin MotteはFreeportの桟橋横の酒場にいました。
>LVは30代のPaladinで、彼を殺すと以下のFactionの変動がありました。
>
>Your faction standing with Steel Warriors got worse.
>Your faction standing with Guards of Qeynos got worse.
>Your faction standing with Corrupt Qeynos Guards got better.
>Your faction standing with The Freeport Militia got better.
>Your faction standing with Knights of Truth got worse.
>
>☆「Head of Sir Edwin Motte」をKazenに渡す。
>
>Kazen Fecae says 'Excellent!' You watch Kazen hold the head by
>the hair and begin to cast a spell. A flash of darkness centers
>around the head and the eyes of the dead knight open, a terrible
>scream emanating from its lips. 'This poor fool here - I think I
>will keep him in my bag from now on. You have done well, my
>new apprentice. Take this symbol and know that you can do
>other tasks to advance within my apprentice ranks.'
>
>You gain experience!!
>
>「Symbol of the Apprentice」が貰えました。
>手に入れたSymbolの名をEmkelに告げることにより、
>そのランクに応じた秘薬の調達を命じられるようです。
</TEXTAREA><br>
